{"tid":2155432,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–抵擋蝗蟲的最新研究","createTime":"2020-08-13T19:16:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T07:47:09.000Z","uid":38861,"like":47,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"56b5326e1ab4cb1bde4c184321aec302c95be4a6","tid":2155432,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T19:16:59.000Z","msg":"除水災外，蝗禍亦會對糧食供應做成極大的傷害。<br />\n<br />\n（圖1）蝗蟲可以分成為兩個形態，獨居形態（Solitary)和群居形態（Gregarious)。當獨居蝗蟲聚集在一起後，牠們身體便會由綠色轉變成黑色，成為群居蝗蟲，同時間亦會在體內產生Phenylacetonitrile (PAN)化學物。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/85vaCzC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F85vaCzC.jpg&h=3a58ed6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n群居蝗蟲受到捕食者攻擊的話，身體裡的PAN化學物便會迅速代謝成為山埃。目的就是如果自己受傷甚至是不幸戰敗的話，對手亦會因為進食自己含有山埃的部份而中毒身亡，玉石俱焚。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2020年8月12日，有科學家在《Science》期刊發表學術文章，講述一道關於蝗蟲的研究。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s41586-020-2610-4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41586-020-2610-4&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBR%2FY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=93eee898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s41586-020-2610-4</a><br />\n<br />\n（圖2）他們發現，若果群居蝗蟲聚集數量多於4隻的話，牠們的身體及糞便會散發出一隻名為4VA（4-Vinylanisole)的化學物。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VLZuS71.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVLZuS71.jpg&h=a56d93cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不論是獨居蝗蟲還是群居蝗蟲，亦不論性別，牠們均會被4VA化學物深深吸引，從而聚集成群，並繼續不斷散發4VA化學物，無止境地召集同伴，建組蝗蟲大軍。<br />\n<br />\n科學家亦發現，蝗蟲觸鬚裡頭名為OR35的嗅覺細胞主力負責感測4VA的存在。當利用基因CRISPR技術移除蝗蟲OR35嗅覺細胞的話，牠們便會失去聚集的能力，進一步確立4VA的重要性；<br />\n目前為止，他們並沒有發現或研發化學物可以抑制蝗蟲的OR35嗅覺細胞。<br />\n<br />\n他們亦嘗試進行實地研究，在野外設立8個含有4VA化學物的捕蝗網。統計過後，捕獲的蝗蟲數量的確有所上升，但並非超級顯著。（圖3）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gLz6Vmp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgLz6Vmp.jpg&h=204d50c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然如此，如果設立的數量足夠的話，不排除可以能夠誘導蝗蟲群組遠離農地，保護農作物。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科普資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。"},{"pid":"166b673dbf2baf36afb7fef29b5c08335808acba","tid":2155432,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T19:17:37.000Z","msg":"<code>Windows Cortana 留名系統啟動，</code><br />\n<code>請勿負評干擾運作。</code>"},{"pid":"dd0aecbf031fde0da3ce7796ee3875abd28257a7","tid":2155432,"uid":165869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T19:19:14.000Z","msg":"薯仔咁夜仲未瞓嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"990137ad6be765fc617cf2f4b709f7650b9d1dff","tid":2155432,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dd0aecbf031fde0da3ce7796ee3875abd28257a7","tid":2155432,"uid":165869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T19:19:14.000Z","msg":"薯仔咁夜仲未瞓嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T19:20:54.000Z","msg":"外國勢力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家晚上十點幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e78c8fcd4546160113200e53d78f59d8f92c0530","tid":2155432,"uid":155238,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T19:21:37.000Z","msg":"呢幾日薯仔做咩咁勤力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪準備又可以每日一篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2b9dd520fcf08da81cd7ec4b91b06388f440d89","tid":2155432,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e78c8fcd4546160113200e53d78f59d8f92c0530","tid":2155432,"uid":155238,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T19:21:37.000Z","msg":"呢幾日薯仔做咩咁勤力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪準備又可以每日一篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" clas