0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T00:26:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />蝗蟲<br />\n話時話年頭好似有蝗蟲要走入中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解冇曬聲氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T04:57:59.000Z","msg":"我都唔太清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，要靠有心晚絲搵真相。"},{"pid":"b2e8c1a32b94ee6cca1645ef089f062d631fa6c2","tid":2155432,"uid":107898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c6eb7f5209beff5e77a6247051d75ee95b0bf13","tid":2155432,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8117a6f4957a9513b851b9b403fe3bf39384f6e6","tid":2155432,"uid":107898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"177eea85e9bc080edcbbeb4761aab4b0cc094b0e","tid":2155432,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T20:33:17.000Z","msg":"依方面應該仲未知，至少文章入面無做到相關實驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T22:00:27.000Z","msg":"4VA唔喺誘捕咋咩<br />\n如果吸多過4隻過嚟<br />\n咪搞到草蜢變蝗蟲<br />\n會唔會弄巧反拙"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T02:17:36.000Z","msg":"其實草蜢同蝗蟲有咩分別"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:03:42.000Z","msg":"草蜢喺獨居蝗蟲，淺綠色<br />\n蝗蟲喺群居蝗蟲，深綠色／黑色"},{"pid":"50fdca7903732408e2c2be6348217397f1ecece0","tid":2155432,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3f37804534968bd6bb68cb699fc089cd5c8b8bcd","tid":2155432,"uid":95577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T00:33:11.000Z","msg":"想問下蝗蟲點樣知自己係4隻以上聚集？<br />\n佢會逐隻數咁？<br />\n<br />\n同埋會變山埃嘅話咪無天敵？<br />\n咁每次蝗災係點樣停？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:10:18.000Z","msg":"實驗做到四隻困埋一齊的話就足夠變，可能係各自散發一啲特別化學物、或者靠互相觸碰而產生變化，我都唔太清楚。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n變山埃真係幾屈機，不過未必個個捕食者都會怕山埃，同埋份量要幾多先會中毒都因動物而異。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都唔知蝗災點搞，人為手法的話可以喺空中噴殺蟲劑，佛系方法應該要靠天氣或者無哂糧食餓死佢哋。<br />\n<br />\n如果他日蝗蟲研究再做深入啲，或者可以基因改造殼物製造一啲對蝗蟲有害但人類無害的物質，唔俾佢哋可以大規模增長。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}